different services and in theory on the long run foodora is better than Uber even if they need support from the company.  I cannot say anything on this since I have never done a gig with any of them.', 'Uber Eats vs. Foodora', ' In this post I bring my point of view on 2 new services that have been recently started in Stockholm.', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '71-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-10-26 21:11:36', '2016-10-26 21:11:36', '', 71, 'https://ivanjr.website/71-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
